===Changes from [[1998 Vodacom Cup|1998]]===
*The {{Rut Namibia Kudus}} joined the competition.
*Section A was renamed Southern Section and Section B was renamed Northern Section.
*The {{Rut Natal Wildebeest}} moved from Section B to the Southern Section.
*{{Rut Griqualand West}} moved from Section A to the Northern Section.

